        {
            "title": "霸王集團發盈警 料上半年轉虧 蝕約490萬元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">霸王集團(01338)發盈警，預期上半年由盈轉虧，將錄得虧損約490萬元人民幣。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司解釋，期內出現虧損，主要因為一種關鍵原材料價格顯著上升，導致毛利率略有下降；另外，公司為了拉動銷售增長，銷售及分銷成本費用顯著上升。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15098611-%e9%9c%b8%e7%8e%8b%e9%9b%86%e5%9c%98%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e8%ad%a6-%e6%96%99%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e8%bd%89%e8%99%a7-%e8%9d%95%e7%b4%84490%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/01338.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-17 17:15:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "誼礫發1995萬元換股債 集資用於開發第3代互聯網Web3.0業務",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">誼礫控股(00076)公布，發行1995萬元換股價予獨立投資者Zhang Yi，集資所得將用於開發公司第3代互聯網Web3.0業務。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述換股債期限為6年，零息；換股價0.25元，較該股今日收市價0.244元溢利2.46%。假設換股價全數被行使，需發新股將佔擴大後股本的15.57%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15098574-%e8%aa%bc%e7%a4%ab%e7%99%bc1995%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%8f%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%82%b5-%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%87%e7%94%a8%e6%96%bc%e9%96%8b%e7%99%bc%e7%ac%ac3%e4%bb%a3%e4%ba%92%e8%81%af%e7%b6%b2web3-0%e6%a5%ad",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/00076.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-17 17:15:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "九興控股上半年收入增0.7% 維持今明兩年派息率約70%的承諾",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">九興控股(01836)公布，上季收入約4.44億美元，按年升2.9%；上半年收入7.75億美元，較去年同期提升0.7%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：九興控股2023年度中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20240422_FI_source-web_01836.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：九興控股2023年度中期報告封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20240422_FI_source-web_01836.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：九興控股2023年度中期報告封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">單計鞋履製造業務，上季收入已達4.33億美元，按年升2.5%；出貨量1540萬雙，增長4.1%，平均售價則按年降1.7%。上半年收入則為7.54億美元，增長0.6%；出貨量2752萬雙，按年升3.8%，平均售價按年降3.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司解釋，期內鞋履製造業務平均售價下降，主要因為均價較低的運動產品訂單佔比較高所致。公司仍預期能繼續實現3年規劃的目標，並承諾在今明兩年派息率維持於70%，另以回購及派特別息向股東返還最多6000萬美元額外現金。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15098546-%e4%b9%9d%e8%88%88%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5%e5%a2%9e0-7-%e7%b6%ad%e6%8c%81%e4%bb%8a%e6%98%8e%e5%85%a9%e5%b9%b4%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af%e7%8e%87%e7%b4%8470%e7%9a%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/01836.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-17 17:00:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "友誼時光發盈喜 料半年轉盈賺最多4400萬元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">友誼時光(06820)發盈喜，預期上半年度扭虧為盈，錄得溢利介乎3800萬元(人民幣．下同)至4400萬元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：友誼時光官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/925x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_06820.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友誼時光官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/925x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_06820.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：友誼時光官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司又估計，期內收益約6億至6.5億元，按年增長14.1%至23.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司解釋，期內業績改善，主要因為新遊戲帶來的收益增量，其中小遊戲《杜拉拉升職記》及《凌雲諾》表現亮眼；加上期內高毛利渠道收入佔比提升，帶動毛利率增約5個百分點；另外，研發費用率和銷售費用率下降，亦有助業績。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15098524-%e5%8f%8b%e8%aa%bc%e6%99%82%e5%85%89%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e5%96%9c-%e6%96%99%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e8%bd%89%e7%9b%88%e8%b3%ba%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a4400%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/06820-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-17 16:50:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
